<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>DAG Builder — Line Engine</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/design.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/jerosoler/Drawflow@0.0.59/dist/drawflow.min.css">
    <style>
        /* viewport-locked 빌더: flex 체인으로 chrome 자동 흡수.
           이전 `height: calc(100vh - 56px - 120px)` 하드코딩은 #207에서 h1을 swe-display-lg(56px)로
           키우면서 toolbar가 ~103px가 됐고, editMode/loadError 배너까지 들어가면 chrome이 가변이라
           아래가 viewport 밖으로 밀려나는데 body overflow:hidden 때문에 스크롤도 못해 잘리던 회귀(#210 후속).
           body는 min-height: 100dvh만 잡고 overflow는 풀어둠 → 정상 viewport는 합산이 정확히 100dvh라
           스크롤바 안 뜨고, 작은 viewport (또는 chrome이 커진 케이스)에선 자연스럽게 body 스크롤 가능. */
        html { height: auto; }
        body {
            min-height: 100dvh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        body > .swe-container {
            flex: 1 1 auto;
            min-height: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .swe-builder-layout {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr 320px;
            gap: var(--space-lg);
            flex: 1 1 auto;
            min-height: 600px;
        }
        .swe-palette, .swe-canvas-wrap, .swe-properties {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 0;
        }

        /* 모바일 overlay 인프라 — 데스크톱/태블릿에선 hidden (override는 mobile @media에서) */
        .swe-mobile-fab-group { display: none; }
        .swe-mobile-backdrop { display: none; }

        /* #205 PR-1 — 반응형 layout (CSS-only). 태블릿은 컬럼만 축소, 모바일은 세로 스택.
           PR-2: 모바일은 palette/properties를 fixed overlay로 빼고 FAB로 토글. */
        @media (max-width: 1023px) and (min-width: 768px) {
            .swe-builder-layout {
                grid-template-columns: 240px 1fr 280px;
                gap: var(--space-md);
            }
        }
        @media (max-width: 767px) {
            .swe-builder-layout {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: var(--space-md);
                min-height: 0;          /* 세로 스택에선 강제 600px 불필요 — body 스크롤로 흡수 */
            }
            /* PR-2: palette/properties는 fixed overlay로 빠짐 → flow에서 제거.
               canvas만 흐름에 남아 flex: 1로 viewport 전체 점유. */
            .swe-canvas-wrap { flex: 1 1 auto; min-height: 60vh; }
            .swe-palette, .swe-properties {
                position: fixed;
                top: 56px;                              /* nav 아래 */
                bottom: 0;
                width: min(85vw, 360px);
                z-index: 1000;                          /* nav(100) 위, 모달(1500) 아래 */
                max-height: none;
                min-height: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
                border-left: none;
                border-right: none;
                box-shadow: 0 0 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
                transition: transform 0.25s ease;
            }
            .swe-palette {
                left: 0;
                transform: translateX(-110%);            /* off-screen 좌측 */
            }
            .swe-properties {
                right: 0;
                transform: translateX(110%);             /* off-screen 우측 */
            }
            .swe-palette.swe-mobile-open,
            .swe-properties.swe-mobile-open {
                transform: translateX(0);
            }

            /* toolbar 가로 분할 깨면서 wrap — h1 + status가 한 줄, 버튼 행이 다음 줄 */
            .swe-builder-toolbar {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
            }
            .swe-builder-toolbar > div:first-child { flex: 1 1 100%; }
            .swe-builder-toolbar .swe-row {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                gap: var(--space-sm);
                width: 100%;
            }
            /* h1 사이즈 다운 — display-lg(56px)는 모바일에서 과함 */
            .swe-builder-toolbar h1.swe-display-lg { font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.25; }
            /* Definition name input 폭 제한 해제 → 가용폭 사용 */
            .swe-builder-toolbar #defNm { width: 100%; min-width: 0; }

            /* 모바일 backdrop — palette/properties 열림 시 표시 */
            .swe-mobile-backdrop {
                display: block;
                position: fixed;
                inset: 56px 0 0 0;
                background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
                z-index: 999;
                opacity: 0;
                visibility: hidden;
                transition: opacity 0.2s ease, visibility 0.2s ease;
            }
            .swe-mobile-backdrop.swe-mobile-open {
                opacity: 1;
                visibility: visible;
            }

            /* FAB — 좌하단 Palette, 우하단 Props */
            .swe-mobile-fab-group {
                display: flex;
                position: fixed;
                bottom: var(--space-md);
                left: 0;
                right: 0;
                justify-content: space-between;
                padding: 0 var(--space-md);
                pointer-events: none;
                z-index: 998;
            }
            .swe-mobile-fab {
                pointer-events: auto;
                background: var(--primary);
                color: var(--on-primary);
                border: none;
                border-radius: var(--radius-md);
                padding: 10px 18px;
                font-size: 14px;
                font-weight: 500;
                font-family: inherit;
                letter-spacing: 0.2px;
                cursor: pointer;
                box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
            }
            .swe-mobile-fab:hover { background: var(--primary-pressed); }
            .swe-mobile-fab:active { transform: translateY(1px); }
            /* panel 열린 동안엔 해당 FAB 숨김 — 중복/오해 방지 */
            .swe-mobile-fab-group.palette-open .swe-mobile-fab[data-fab="palette"],
            .swe-mobile-fab-group.properties-open .swe-mobile-fab[data-fab="properties"] {
                visibility: hidden;
            }
        }
        .swe-panel-header {
            padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline);
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--mute);
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            background: var(--surface-elevated);
        }
        .swe-panel-body {
            flex: 1;
            overflow: auto;
            padding: var(--space-md);
        }
        .swe-palette-item {
            background: var(--surface-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
            margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
            cursor: grab;
            font-size: 13px;
            user-select: none;
        }
        .swe-palette-item:hover { border-color: var(--hairline-strong); background: var(--surface-elevated); }
        .swe-palette-item .meta { font-size: 11px; color: var(--mute); margin-top: 2px; }
        /* #192 — @Activity(description) 메타 노출. 1~2줄 요약, 길면 ellipsis (hover 시 title로 풀텍스트). */
        .swe-palette-item .desc {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--body);
            margin-top: 2px;
            line-height: 1.4;
            display: -webkit-box;
            -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        #drawflow {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle, var(--hairline) 1px, transparent 1px) 0 0 / 24px 24px,
                var(--canvas);
            /* #205 PR-3 — Drawflow 내부 터치 핸들러에 모든 gesture 위임.
               touch-action: none이면 브라우저 pan/zoom 안 일어남 → Drawflow의 1-finger 노드 드래그 /
               2-finger 핀치줌이 충돌 없이 동작. body 영역 밖 스크롤엔 영향 없음 (canvas만 적용). */
            touch-action: none;
        }

        /* touch device — 포트 hit area 키움 (#205 PR-3). pointer: coarse는 stylus/finger 등 정밀도 낮은 입력 매체.
           desktop 마우스(fine)는 18px 유지, 손가락은 22px로 확장. */
        @media (pointer: coarse) {
            .drawflow .drawflow-node .input,
            .drawflow .drawflow-node .output {
                width: 22px;
                height: 22px;
            }
        }
        /* position: absolute는 Drawflow 기본 — 절대 덮어쓰지 말 것.
           이전에 exec-order-badge anchor용으로 position:relative를 추가했다가 노드 좌표가 block flow로
           세로 stacking되어 화살표/포트 위치가 모든 시점에서 어긋나던 회귀(#191/#200/#203의 진짜 원인)를 유발. */
        .drawflow .drawflow-node {
            background: var(--surface-elevated);
            border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
            color: var(--ink);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: var(--space-md);
            min-width: 180px;
            box-shadow: none;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .drawflow .drawflow-node.selected { border-color: var(--primary); }
        /* #135 — 좌측 stations list 클릭 시 캔버스 노드를 강조 */
        .drawflow .drawflow-node.builder-focused {
            border-color: var(--line-yellow, #FBCA04);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--line-yellow, #FBCA04), 0 0 12px rgba(251, 202, 4, 0.5);
        }

        /* #130 — 포트(input/output) 큼지막하게 + hover 시 강조해 드래그 시작점 명확화 */
        .drawflow .drawflow-node .input,
        .drawflow .drawflow-node .output {
            background: var(--surface-card);
            border: 2px solid var(--hairline-strong);
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
            cursor: crosshair;
            transition: transform 0.1s ease, border-color 0.1s ease, background 0.1s ease;
        }
        .drawflow .drawflow-node .output:hover,
        .drawflow .drawflow-node .input:hover {
            transform: scale(1.35);
            border-color: var(--accent-pink);
            background: var(--accent-pink);
        }

        /* #197 — output 드래그 시작 시 다른 노드의 input 포트를 글로우 펄스로 강조 (drop-target affordance) */
        .drawflow .drawflow-node .input.drop-target {
            border-color: var(--line-brand, #59d499);
            animation: drop-target-pulse 1.4s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes drop-target-pulse {
            0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(230, 25, 127, 0.25); }
            50%      { box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(230, 25, 127, 0.50); }
        }
        @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
            .drawflow .drawflow-node .input.drop-target {
                animation: none;
                box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(230, 25, 127, 0.40);
            }
        }
        .drawflow .drawflow-node .input.drop-target:hover {
            background: var(--line-brand, #59d499);
        }

        /* 엣지 — 방향 화살표 추가 */
        .drawflow .connection .main-path {
            stroke: var(--mute);
            stroke-width: 2;
            marker-end: url(#dag-edge-arrow);
        }
        .drawflow .connection.selected .main-path {
            stroke: var(--primary);
            marker-end: url(#dag-edge-arrow-selected);
        }

        .swe-builder-toolbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
            gap: var(--space-md);
        }
        .swe-builder-status {
            color: var(--mute);
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .swe-validation-list { font-size: 12px; color: var(--accent-red); }

        /* #152 — 조건식 있는 엣지: dashed line + 작은 라벨 */
        .drawflow .connection.has-condition .main-path {
            stroke-dasharray: 6 4;
            stroke: var(--accent-yellow, #FBCA04);
        }
        .drawflow .connection.has-condition.selected .main-path {
            stroke: var(--primary);
        }
        .swe-edge-cond-label {
            position: absolute;
            background: var(--surface-elevated);
            border: 1px solid var(--accent-yellow, #FBCA04);
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            padding: 2px 6px;
            font-size: 10px;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            color: var(--ink);
            white-space: nowrap;
            max-width: 220px;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 4;
        }

        /* 조건식 편집 모달 */
        #edge-cond-backdrop {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
            z-index: 1500;
        }
        #edge-cond-modal {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 560px;
            max-width: 90vw;
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            padding: var(--space-lg);
            z-index: 1600;
        }

        /* #151 — 단축키 cheatsheet modal */
        #shortcuts-backdrop {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
            z-index: 1500;
        }
        #shortcuts-modal {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 480px;
            max-width: 90vw;
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            padding: var(--space-lg);
            z-index: 1600;
        }
        #shortcuts-modal table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px; }
        #shortcuts-modal td { padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-xs); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline); }
        #shortcuts-modal td:first-child { width: 140px; }
        #shortcuts-modal kbd {
            background: var(--surface-elevated);
            border: 1px solid var(--hairline-strong);
            border-bottom-width: 2px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            padding: 2px 6px;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: var(--ink);
        }
        .swe-shortcut-hint {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-left: var(--space-sm);
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 10px;
            color: var(--mute);
            opacity: 0.75;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<!-- Drawflow SVG 엣지에 적용할 화살표 marker. 모든 connection .main-path가 marker-end로 참조. -->
<svg width="0" height="0" style="position:absolute" aria-hidden="true">
    <defs>
        <marker id="dag-edge-arrow" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="10" refY="5"
                markerWidth="8" markerHeight="8" orient="auto-start-reverse">
            <path d="M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z" fill="currentColor" style="fill: var(--mute);"/>
        </marker>
        <marker id="dag-edge-arrow-selected" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="10" refY="5"
                markerWidth="8" markerHeight="8" orient="auto-start-reverse">
            <path d="M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z" style="fill: var(--primary);"/>
        </marker>
    </defs>
</svg>

{{> _nav }}

<div class="swe-container" style="padding-top: var(--space-xxl); padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);">
    <div class="swe-builder-toolbar">
        <div>
            <h1 class="swe-display-lg" style="margin: 0;">
                {{#editMode}}Edit Line — {{definitionNm}} <span class="swe-mute" style="font-size: 13px;">v{{versionNo}}</span>{{/editMode}}
                {{^editMode}}DAG Builder{{/editMode}}
            </h1>
            <div class="swe-builder-status" id="status">
                {{#editMode}}Editing existing line · changes replace nodes/edges in place (same ID, same version){{/editMode}}
                {{^editMode}}Ready · 좌측에서 활동을 캔버스로 드래그 · 노드 우측 ● 포트에서 다른 노드의 좌측 ● 포트로 드래그하면 연결{{/editMode}}
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="swe-row">
            <input id="defNm" class="swe-input" style="width: 200px;" placeholder="Definition name" value="{{#editMode}}{{definitionNm}}{{/editMode}}" {{#editMode}}readonly title="Definition name 변경은 새 정의 생성으로 — 편집에선 read-only"{{/editMode}}>
            {{#editMode}}<a href="/line/definitions/{{definitionId}}" class="swe-btn-tertiary">Cancel</a>{{/editMode}}
            {{^editMode}}<button class="swe-btn-tertiary" onclick="clearAll()">Clear</button>{{/editMode}}
            <button type="button" class="swe-btn-tertiary" onclick="openShortcutsModal()" title="Keyboard shortcuts (?)">⌨ <span class="swe-shortcut-hint">?</span></button>
            <button class="swe-btn-primary" onclick="saveDefinition()">Save</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    {{#editMode}}
    <div class="swe-card swe-mb-lg" style="padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg); border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-yellow);">
        <strong>편집 모드</strong> — 저장하면 같은 ID로 역/엣지를 통째로 교체합니다.
        진행 중 인스턴스가 있다면 후행 단계가 새 정의 기준으로 동작할 수 있으니 주의.
        새 버전을 만들고 싶으면 <a href="/line/builder">신규 생성</a>으로.
    </div>
    {{/editMode}}

    <!-- #206 — Line settings(SLA/Concurrency/Tags)는 우측 Properties 패널의 탭으로 이동.
         페이지 상단 영역을 회수해 캔버스 가용 공간을 늘림. 노드 비선택 시 Line settings가
         자연스럽게 보이고, 노드 선택 시 Properties 탭으로 자동 전환. -->
    {{#loadError}}
    <div class="swe-card swe-mb-lg" style="padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg); border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-pink);">
        <strong>로드 실패:</strong> {{loadError}}
    </div>
    {{/loadError}}

    <div class="swe-builder-layout">
        <!-- Left: palette + stations list (tabbed — #135 D1=b) -->
        <aside class="swe-palette">
            <div class="swe-tab-bar" role="tablist">
                <button type="button" class="swe-tab active" id="tab-activities"
                        role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="palette"
                        onclick="switchTab('activities')">Activities</button>
                <button type="button" class="swe-tab" id="tab-stations"
                        role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="stations-tab-body"
                        onclick="switchTab('stations')">Stations <span id="stations-count" class="swe-mute" style="font-size:11px;"></span></button>
            </div>
            <div class="swe-panel-body" id="palette" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-activities">
                <div class="swe-mute" style="font-size: 12px;">Loading…</div>
            </div>
            <div class="swe-panel-body" id="stations-tab-body" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-stations" style="display: none;">
                <div class="swe-station-list-search">
                    <input type="text" id="stations-search" placeholder="역 이름 / activity 검색…" aria-label="Stations 검색">
                </div>
                <div class="swe-station-list" id="stations-list">
                    <div class="swe-station-list-empty">아직 역이 없습니다 — Activities 탭에서 드래그하세요.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </aside>

        <!-- Center: canvas -->
        <main class="swe-canvas-wrap">
            <div class="swe-panel-header">Canvas — drag nodes from left, click two nodes to connect</div>
            <div id="drawflow"></div>
        </main>

        <!-- Right: properties + line settings (#206 — tabbed) -->
        <aside class="swe-properties">
            <div class="swe-tab-bar" role="tablist">
                <button type="button" class="swe-tab" id="tab-props"
                        role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="props"
                        onclick="switchPropTab('props')">Properties</button>
                <button type="button" class="swe-tab active" id="tab-line-settings"
                        role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="line-settings-body"
                        onclick="switchPropTab('line-settings')">Line settings</button>
            </div>
            <div class="swe-panel-body" id="props" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-props" style="display: none;">
                <div class="swe-mute" style="font-size: 12px;">Click a node to edit its inputParams</div>
            </div>
            <div class="swe-panel-body" id="line-settings-body" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-line-settings">
                <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-md);">
                    <div>
                        <label for="slaSeconds">Max duration (seconds)</label>
                        <input type="number" id="slaSeconds" class="swe-input" min="1" step="1"
                               placeholder="예: 3600 (1시간)"
                               value="{{#slaSeconds}}{{slaSeconds}}{{/slaSeconds}}">
                        <div class="swe-mute" style="font-size: 11px; margin-top: 4px;">
                            인스턴스 시작 후 N초 넘으면 SLA 위반. 비워두면 SLA 비활성.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="slaAction">Action on violation</label>
                        <select id="slaAction" class="swe-input">
                            <option value="">— select —</option>
                            <option value="ALERT_ONLY" {{#slaActionAlert}}selected{{/slaActionAlert}}>ALERT_ONLY (알림만, 인스턴스 진행)</option>
                            <option value="AUTO_TERMINATE" {{#slaActionTerminate}}selected{{/slaActionTerminate}}>AUTO_TERMINATE (알림 + 인스턴스 종료)</option>
                        </select>
                        <div class="swe-mute" style="font-size: 11px; margin-top: 4px;">
                            위반 시 webhook으로 알림 (engine.sla.webhook-url). 인스턴스 RunOptions로 override 가능.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- #141 — 동시 실행 정책 -->
                    <div>
                        <label for="concurrencyPolicy">Concurrency policy</label>
                        <select id="concurrencyPolicy" class="swe-input">
                            <option value="" {{#concurrencyConcurrent}}selected{{/concurrencyConcurrent}}>CONCURRENT (default)</option>
                            <option value="SKIP_IF_RUNNING" {{#concurrencySkip}}selected{{/concurrencySkip}}>SKIP_IF_RUNNING</option>
                            <option value="PIPELINE_1" {{#concurrencyPipeline1}}selected{{/concurrencyPipeline1}}>PIPELINE_1</option>
                            <option value="PIPELINE_2" {{#concurrencyPipeline2}}selected{{/concurrencyPipeline2}}>PIPELINE_2</option>
                            <option value="PIPELINE_3" {{#concurrencyPipeline3}}selected{{/concurrencyPipeline3}}>PIPELINE_3</option>
                        </select>
                        <div class="swe-mute" style="font-size: 11px; margin-top: 4px;">
                            CONCURRENT: 같은 정의 인스턴스 동시 실행 허용.<br>
                            SKIP_IF_RUNNING: RUNNING/PAUSED 있으면 새 시작 무시 (cron 적체 방지).<br>
                            PIPELINE_N: 활동 단위 단계 동기화 (#164).
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- #142 — 태그 -->
                    <div>
                        <label for="tagsInput">Tags</label>
                        <input type="text" id="tagsInput" class="swe-input" placeholder="etl, daily, finance"
                               value="{{#tagsCsv}}{{tagsCsv}}{{/tagsCsv}}">
                        <div class="swe-mute" style="font-size: 11px; margin-top: 4px;">
                            쉼표로 구분 (free-form). 자동 trim + lowercase. 목록에서 필터/검색.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </aside>
    </div>

    <div id="validation" class="swe-card swe-validation-list" style="margin-top: var(--space-lg); display: none;"></div>
</div>

<!-- #205 PR-2 — 모바일 overlay 인프라 (데스크톱/태블릿에선 CSS로 숨김) -->
<div class="swe-mobile-backdrop" id="mobile-backdrop" onclick="closeMobilePanels()" aria-hidden="true"></div>
<div class="swe-mobile-fab-group" id="mobile-fab-group" aria-hidden="false">
    <button type="button" class="swe-mobile-fab" data-fab="palette"
            onclick="toggleMobilePanel('palette')" aria-label="Open palette panel">☰ Palette</button>
    <button type="button" class="swe-mobile-fab" data-fab="properties"
            onclick="toggleMobilePanel('properties')" aria-label="Open properties panel">⚙ Props</button>
</div>

<!-- #136 — 떠다니는 컨텍스트 메뉴 (노드/엣지 우클릭) -->
<ul id="ctx-menu" class="swe-ctx-menu" role="menu" tabindex="-1" aria-label="Context menu" style="display:none;"></ul>

<!-- #151 — 단축키 cheatsheet -->
<div id="shortcuts-backdrop"></div>
<div id="shortcuts-modal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="shortcuts-title">
    <div class="swe-flex-between swe-mb-md">
        <h3 id="shortcuts-title" class="swe-heading-md" style="margin:0;">Keyboard shortcuts</h3>
        <button type="button" class="swe-btn-tertiary swe-btn-sm" onclick="closeShortcutsModal()">✕</button>
    </div>
    <table>
        <tbody>
        <tr><td><kbd>Del</kbd> / <kbd>Backspace</kbd></td><td>선택된 노드 삭제 (엣지 자동 정리)</td></tr>
        <tr><td><kbd>Esc</kbd></td><td>Connect 모드 취소 / 메뉴·모달 닫기</td></tr>
        <tr><td><kbd>F</kbd></td><td>Stations 탭 + 검색 input 포커스</td></tr>
        <tr><td><kbd>?</kbd> / <kbd>Shift</kbd>+<kbd>/</kbd></td><td>이 cheatsheet 토글</td></tr>
        <tr><td><kbd>Ctrl</kbd>+<kbd>S</kbd></td><td>Save (브라우저 기본 차단)</td></tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
    <div class="swe-mute" style="font-size: 11px; margin-top: var(--space-md); line-height: 1.5;">
        input/textarea 포커스 시 단축키 비활성 (텍스트 입력 우선). 모달 열린 상태에선 <kbd>Esc</kbd>만 동작.
    </div>
</div>

<!-- #152 — 엣지 조건식 편집 모달 -->
<div id="edge-cond-backdrop"></div>
<div id="edge-cond-modal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="edge-cond-title">
    <div class="swe-flex-between swe-mb-xl">
        <h3 id="edge-cond-title" class="swe-heading-md" style="margin:0;">Edit edge condition (SpEL)</h3>
        <button type="button" class="swe-btn-tertiary swe-btn-sm" onclick="closeEdgeCondModal()">✕</button>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">
        <div id="edge-cond-info" class="swe-mute" style="font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: var(--space-md); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;"></div>
        <label for="edge-cond-input" style="display:block; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:var(--space-xs);">SpEL 조건식</label>
        <textarea id="edge-cond-input" rows="4"
                  placeholder='#result["success"] == true'
                  style="width:100%; padding:var(--space-sm); background:var(--surface-elevated); border:1px solid var(--hairline); color:var(--ink); border-radius:var(--radius-sm); font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.9em;"></textarea>
        <div class="swe-mute" style="font-size: 11px; margin-top: var(--space-xs); line-height: 1.5;">
            활동 결과 JSON은 <code>#result</code>로 접근. 예시:<br>
            <code>#result['success'] == true</code> · <code>#result['count'] &gt; 10</code> · <code>#result['status'] == 'OK' and #result['errors'] == 0</code><br>
            빈 값으로 두면 조건 없이 진행. 모든 outgoing의 조건이 false면 인스턴스가 FAILED 처리됨 (#152).
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="edge-cond-error" style="display:none; color:var(--accent-pink); font-size:13px; margin-top:var(--space-md);"></div>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:var(--space-md); margin-top:var(--space-lg); justify-content:space-between;">
        <button type="button" class="swe-btn-tertiary swe-btn-danger" onclick="clearEdgeCond()">Clear condition</button>
        <div style="display:flex; gap:var(--space-md);">
            <button type="button" class="swe-btn-tertiary" onclick="closeEdgeCondModal()">Cancel</button>
            <button type="button" class="swe-btn-primary" onclick="saveEdgeCond()">Save</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

{{#existingDefinitionJson}}
<script id="existing-definition-json" type="application/json">{{{existingDefinitionJson}}}</script>
{{/existingDefinitionJson}}

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/jerosoler/Drawflow@0.0.59/dist/drawflow.min.js"></script>
<script src="/js/subway-map.js"></script>

<!-- #181 PR-1 — Builder JS는 /js/builder/index.js로 외부화. 서버 주입값은 data-island 사용. -->
<script id="builder-config" type="application/json">
{
    "editMode": {{#editMode}}true{{/editMode}}{{^editMode}}false{{/editMode}},
    "editDefinitionId": {{#editMode}}"{{definitionId}}"{{/editMode}}{{^editMode}}null{{/editMode}}
}
</script>
<!-- #181 PR-1~4 모듈 — load order:
     pure helpers → IO/직렬화 → UI 모듈(state 선언) → entrypoint (editor 생성 + 부트스트랩).
     classic script global scope 공유: 모든 함수가 호출 시점에 globals lookup → safe. -->
<script src="/js/builder/graph-model.js" defer></script>
<script src="/js/builder/form-serializer.js" defer></script>
<script src="/js/builder/mobile-overlay.js" defer></script>
<script src="/js/builder/shortcuts.js" defer></script>
<script src="/js/builder/ctx-menu.js" defer></script>
<script src="/js/builder/touch-longpress.js" defer></script>
<script src="/js/builder/edge-condition-modal.js" defer></script>
<script src="/js/builder/index.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
